Projects

Data Analysis

Language : C

Provides functions for data analysis and statistics purposes. The functions are designed to analyzing datasets organized as columns and can calculate various statistics, such as mean, minimum, maximum, standard deviation, median, quartiles, and can also remove extreme values.

Autonomous robot project

Language : Embedded C

Programming of an autonomous object-finder robot project. The robot is powered by a PIC18 microcontroller, and is equipped with a sonar sensor to detect its surroundings, and two tracks to move.

Predictive text recognition

Language : C, css

Creation of a human-machine interface that provides suggestions based on incomplete user input. The most frequent words are priorized as suggestions. The user has the option to manually add new words.
